---
title: "首页"
---
{% extends "base.njk" %}

{% block content %}
<div class="meta-block">
  <div class="eyebrow">参考手册</div>
  <h1>产品经理工作流</h1>
  <div class="desc">覆盖从发现问题到迭代优化的完整闭环，每个阶段配有可直接使用的 AI 技能。</div>
  <div class="meta">6 个阶段 · 40+ 技能 · 14 个工具</div>
</div>

<section style="margin-bottom:40px;">
  <h2 style="font-size:1.0625rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--ink);margin-bottom:16px;padding-bottom:8px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);">阶段</h2>
  <div class="phase-list">
    {%- for p in phases %}
    <a href="/{{ p.id }}/" class="phase-list-item">
      <span class="phase-list-num dot-{{ p.id }}" style="background:var(--clr-{{ p.id }});"></span>
      <div class="phase-list-body">
        <div class="phase-list-header">
          <h3>{{ p.name }}</h3>
          <span class="phase-list-short">{{ p.short }}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="phase-list-question">{{ p.question }}</div>
        <div class="phase-list-output">产出：{{ p.output }}</div>
      </div>
      <span class="phase-list-arrow">→</span>
    </a>
    {%- endfor %}
  </div>
</section>

<div class="quick-start">
  <h2>快速上手</h2>
  <div class="quick-start-grid">
    <div class="quick-start-item">
      <span class="qs-command">/interview-synthesis</span>
      <span class="qs-desc">日常需求评审，输入原始访谈记录</span>
    </div>
    <div class="quick-start-item">
      <span class="qs-command">/prd</span>
      <span class="qs-desc">写 PRD，vibe coding 场景</span>
    </div>
    <div class="quick-start-item">
      <span class="qs-command">/vibe-prd-writer</span>
      <span class="qs-desc">完整项目规范，直接喂给 Claude Code</span>
    </div>
    <div class="quick-start-item">
      <span class="qs-command">/meeting-to-action</span>
      <span class="qs-desc">整理会议纪要，提取行动项</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
{% endblock %}
